    <string name="about_focuslife_dialog_title">About FocusLife</string>
    <string name="about_focuslife_body">FocusLife is a companion app for building a balanced lifestyle: tracking health, nutrition, food diary, focus sessions, movement and personal goals.\n\nThe app is designed around a simple message: improve a little every day, live with more focus, take better care of your body, and love yourself through small consistent actions.\n\nCreated by:\nNguyễn Ngọc Thiện - 23110154\nNghiêm Phú Đăng Quân - 23110144\nNguyễn Quốc Khoa - 23110116\n\nThe authors are students of Ho Chi Minh City University of Technology and Education (HCMUTE).\n\nThis is a Mobile Programming course project instructed by Master Trương Thị Ngọc Phượng.</string>
