Students of Ho Chi Minh City University of Technology and Education (HCMUTE).</string>
    <string name="about_focuslife_course_title">Academic project</string>
    <string name="about_focuslife_course_body">This application was developed as a Mobile Programming course project under the guidance of Master Trương Thị Ngọc Phượng. It reflects the team effort to combine usability, thoughtful UI and positive lifestyle values into one product.</string>
